<dl id="n31080e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n31" href="#n31080e">N31 (VI.B.26)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n31all.htm#n31080e"> 80(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> purdah (veil) </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Purdah: a curtain, esp. one to screen women from the sight of men. Persian <i>pardah</i>: veil, curtain.  <br>Raphael transcription: <a name="c10127d" href="c10all.htm#c10127d">VI.C.10:127(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
